rows.label: qst701805_msg0001
rows.name:
Three Golden Sand Cocoons and
three Cotton Branches...

rows.label: qst701805_msg0002
rows.name:
And then two Bladed Holly
twigs... was that it?

rows.label: qst701805_msg0003
rows.name:
I don't know how to use them,
but if Kasumi-san says so, they
must be important materials.

rows.label: qst701805_msg0004
rows.name:
Among them, the Golden Sand Cocoon
seems to be a very precious thing.

rows.label: qst701805_msg0005
rows.name:
I've heard from Adel-sama before that it's
the cocoon of a rare insect that lives in
a place called the Streamsand Corridor.

rows.label: qst701805_msg0006
rows.name:
I'm sorry to bother you at a time
like this, but I really want to
overcome my weakness in embroidery.

rows.label: qst701805_msg0007
rows.name:
I'll do my best as
Kasumi-san says! Please!
